**Findings**

- `[P0]` [CanvasPage.tsx](C:\Users\sahil\OneDrive\Documents\GitHub\Mechanize_takehome\client\src\components\CanvasPage.tsx#L615): integration still does not honor server-authoritative ordering. Concurrent conflicting edits can leave one client with a different final state than the server and the other peers.
